//ma.aseantradecenter.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"keyl<em></em>ink\">磨具</span></a>、刀具、工夹具及相关产品、检验和测量设备。\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	展位价格：\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	国内	国外\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	光地（18平米起）	1,272元/平米	2,310元/平米\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	标展（9平米起）	1,590元/平米	2,883元/平米\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	知名展商：\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	金切：山崎马扎克、哈斯、沈阳机床、大连光洋、济二机床、秦川机床、北京二机床、汉川机床、大正、伟力、治丞、桂北等\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	成形：通快、天田、萨瓦尼尼、埃威迪、团结普瑞马、三菱、罗芬、麦格菲、村田、韩光、相干、偲丹、百克、台励福、梁发记、扬力、亚威、金方圆、华工、楚天、大族、捷迈、迪能、飞虎、镭鸣、迅镭、宏山、金运等\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	其他：福禄水刀、大地水刀、奥拓福水刀、OMAX、哈格、阿库、超技、基恩士、普威特、悦瑞、形创、株钻、博特、威库斯、kasto、气力等。\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	参展程序:&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	1、完整填写并提交参展申请表\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	2、与主办方确认展位和费用\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#454545;font-size:16px;\">\r\n	3、签订正式的参展合同并按照合同条款支付展位费\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:微软雅黑